<H3> <TI>   Government Approves Attorney General Appointment </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Approves Attorney General Appointment </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0405171094 Prague CTK in English 1448 GMT 4 May 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU0405171094 </F>
<F P=104>  Prague CTK </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Prague, May 4 (CTK) -- The Czech Government today 
unanimously approved Bohumira Kopecna into the post of the Czech 
attorney general, Prime Minister Vaclav Klaus told journalists 
after the government session. The government is glad that a 
woman will hold a more significant post in the state 
administration, Klaus added. Kopecna has so far been heading 
the Attorney General's Office as deputy attorney general. 

</TEXT>

