<H3> <TI>   Foreign Ministry Welcomes PLO-Israeli Accord </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Ministry Welcomes PLO-Israeli Accord </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0405161194 Prague CTK in English 1536 GMT 4 May 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU0405161194 </F>
<F P=104>  Prague CTK </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Prague, May 4 (CTK) -- The Czech Foreign Ministry 
was pleased to learn about the agreement on limited Palestinian 
self-rule signed today in Cairo between PLO leader Yasir 'Arafat 
and Israeli Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin. The document is a 
further important step on the road towards permanent peace in 
the Middle East, a ministry statement says. 

</TEXT>

