<DOCNO> FBIS4-54805 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreeu087_b_94006" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EEU-94-087 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  3 May 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> BULGARIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Indonesian Foreign Minister Arrives on Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Indonesian Foreign Minister Arrives on Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0305172894 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1600 
GMT 3 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0305172894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Bulgarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] I am very pleased to have the opportunity to visit 
Bulgaria, something that I have wanted to do for a long time, 
said Indonesian Foreign Minister Ali Abdullah Alatas upon his 
arrival. During his meetings in Sofia he will mainly discuss 
issues connected with developing economic contacts, because no 
controversial problems exist in political relations between 
Bulgaria and Indonesia. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

