BFN 

  [Text] Sarajevo, May 4 (AFP) -- In a statement released in 
Bonn prior to news of the gunshots, German Foreign Minister 
Klaus Kinkel described the despatch of the ambassador as "a 
further signal of our efforts to bring peace and stability to 
Bosnia-Herzegovina". An important aspect of the German 
