<H3> <TI>   Parties Request `Expulsion' of Greek Priest </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Parties Request `Expulsion' of Greek Priest </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0405175294 Tirana ATA in English 1202 GMT 4 May 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU0405175294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana ATA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tirana, May 4 (ATA) -- The National Association of 
the Former Political Prisoners and the Persecuted Ones, the 
Party of Balli Kombetar [National Front], the Albanian People's 
League Party, the Albanian Union Democratic Movement, the 
Ecological Party, and other parties consider the existence of 
the Greek priest, Anastas Janullatos, at the head of the 
Albanian Autocephalous Orthodox Church as completely 
inappropriate and demand his expulsion. 
  The above political parties and associations support the 
Committee for the Defence of the Autocephalous Orthodox Church 
of Albania which has accused the Greek Government of 
interference into the internal affairs of the Albanian state and 
of the Albanian Autocephalous Church on the eve of Easter, 
through Anastas Janullatos, who is considered by this committee 
as "a foreign and illegal archbishop." 
  Statements in support of the Autocephalous character of the 
Albanian Orthodox Church have been made during Easter also by 
the Democratic Party and the Republican one. 

</TEXT>

