  Electoral preferences are cited only for those political 
entities that would receive in April at least 1.5 percent of the 
vote of adult citizens of the Slovak Republic who are either 
determined to vote or will probably vote. The APR and the 
NDS-NA did not operate as independent political entities at the 
time of the March poll (2-10 March), while the Association of 
Workers of Slovakia had not yet declared itself a political 
entity. 

