<F P=106> [TA SR report: "Netherlands Embassy"] </F>
  [Text] A reception on the occasion of the Netherlands 
national day, the Day of the Queen, hosted by Hans J. Heinemann, 
ambassador of the Kingdom of the Netherlands to the Slovak 
Republic resident in Prague, marked the official opening of an 
independent representative office of the Kingdom of the 
Netherlands in Bratislava. The embassy's task is to intensify 
contacts between the two countries. Initially, the Kingdom of 
the Netherlands will be represented in Slovakia by Charge 
D'Affaires Hugo Gajus Scheltema. 

