<H3> <TI>   HSP Leader Horn Injured in Car Accident </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    HSP Leader Horn Injured in Car Accident </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0505204294 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network in Hungarian 
2000 GMT 5 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0505204294 </F>
<F P=104>  Budapest Kossuth Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Hungarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] We have just received the news that Gyula Horn has 
been involved in an accident. Peter Juhasz reports: 
  [Juhasz] Not long after 2100, Gyula Horn, chairman of the 
Hungarian Socialist Party [HSP], who was on his way home after 
his end of campaign mass rally in Miskolc, has been in an 
accident. 
  Details are not known thus far. All I managed to find out a 
few minutes ago was that Gyula Horn's car crashed into a truck 
that did not have its lights on while passing on the No. 3 main 
trunk road between Nyekladhaza and Emoed. Three people were 
injured in the crash, including the party chairman. How and to 
what extent are not yet known. 
  Anyway, preparations have already been made at the trauma 
department of the Miskolc Iron Works Hospital to receive the 
injured. 

</TEXT>

