<H3> <TI>   SZDSZ Contradicts MSZP on Debt Issue </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    SZDSZ Contradicts MSZP on Debt Issue </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94CH0247A Budapest PESTI HIRLAP in Hungarian 21 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 94CH0247A </F>
<F P=104>  Budapest PESTI HIRLAP </F>
<F P=105>  Hungarian </F>


<TEXT>
CSO 

<F P=106> [Unattributed article: "Statement by Alliance of Free </F>
Democrats Professionals: Insolvency Is Out of Question"] 
  [Text] SZDSZ [Alliance of Free Democrats] Representatives 
Gyula Gaal, Karoly Attila Soos, and Marton Tardos had this to 
say: "At a news conference on 19 April, Gyula Horn and Laszlo 
Bekesi (...) mentioned that a threat of insolvency exists in 
Hungary. We regard this supposition as unfortunate and 
groundless, the same way as we regard the shrill sound of the 
government's success propaganda coming from the other side. The 
fact is that the MNB [Hungarian National Bank] is successful in 
floating bonds in the international market place, and this 
fact--indicating confidence in our country--has not been changed 
even by the extraordinarily grave deterioration of our 
international balance of payments last year. (...) There is no 
basis for leaders of a party that prepares itself to play a role 
in governance, and to direct long-term processes, to make the 
above-quoted, oddly pessimistic statement." 

</TEXT>

