  [Excerpt] The Independent Smallholders Party [FKGP] is also 
assessing the chances of the second round of the election and 
hopes that in three weeks' time it will be able to overtake the 
Hungarian Democratic Forum [MDF]. Agnes Pap reports: 
  [Pap] The Smallholders are satisfied with the first round of 
the elections and are expecting the position of the parties in 
third and fourth place to change on 29 May, in other words that 
the FKGP will overtake the MDF and will be one of those to stand 
