<H3> <TI>   Solidarity Strike Spreads </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Solidarity Strike Spreads </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0705083794 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 0800 
GMT 7 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0705083794 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network </F>
<F P=105>  Polish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Solidarity's protest action is continuing. At 0900, 
Solidarity employees at the Czestochowa Steelworks 
[central-southern Poland] staged a two-hour strike. The 
Solidarity regional board did not receive notification of strike 
participation by other factories in Czestochowa Province. 
  In the central-eastern region of Poland, the work-force of 
the Communications Equipment Plant in Swidnik, the scales 
factory in Lublin, and the rolling bearings factory in Krasnik 
joined the strike today. 

</TEXT>

